      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) agrees with experimental measurements within 15% across all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH values compared against in-vitro hemolysis measurements at all five operating points. Maximum deviation was 11.4% at the 3 L/min, 3500 RPM condition; mean absolute error was 7.8%. All comparisons satisfy the Gradation 2 output comparison criterion."
