    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scope. CFD-predicted NIH values agree with in-vitro measurements within 11.4% across all operating points, and the relative hemolysis index RH is less than 1.0 at all five flow-speed combinations. The model is accepted as fit for the COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
